#razr\xc2\xa0#FlipYourLook\xc2\xa0challenge\xc2\xa0:growing_heart:

Turning looks, stunting pretty... it\xe2\x80\x99s the queen from New York City coming at you for the final week of the\xc2\xa0#razr\xc2\xa0#FlipYourLook\xc2\xa0fashion\xc2\xa0challenge!! A drag queen telling you to head to the closet is almost unheard of, but I can\xe2\x80\x99t wait wait to see all the fierce looks you turn\xc2\xa0out!\xc2\xa0#MotoPartner
Here\xe2\x80\x99s all the tea and details:
1. Post your fiercest Spring Cleaning inspired look. Re-style, re-purpose, and re-imagine your favorite garments and accessories in a fierce new way!

b"Need to disinfect your phone?

Here's how:
Turn it off and use wipes with 70% isopropyl alcohol on your device. Avoid the charging port, headphone jack, mics and speakers. Also, don't submerge or directly spray your phone with cleaners, and don't use bleach or abrasives.

For more, visit motorola.com or local health authorities like the CDC."
